{
  "texts": [
    "The additional links serve as shortcuts to the mesh design to support intra-layer traffic.",
    "3) Atleus: Atleus, unlike previous configurations, does not incorporate a 3D-mesh.",
    "As explained in section IV, we utilize different interconnect strategies for ReRAM and systolic array tiers.",
    "Specifically, we utilize an SFC to connect cores in the ReRAM tier given the unidirectional flow of activations among consecutive neural layers.",
    "Conversely, we employ a mesh interconnect for the systolic array tier, where both input data and output activations flow."
  ]
}